308861953.name: XY—Steam Siege
308861953.description: Long years of stability come to an end when Shiny Mega Gardevoir-EX lays siege to the mighty Gear Palace with a host of greedy forces. The Mythical Steam Pokémon Volcanion must wield the dual powers of fire and water to stop them! As the battle rages, Xerneas BREAK and Yveltal BREAK face off in the Pokémon TCG: XY—Steam Siege expansion!

308861954.name: XY—Steam Siege
308861954.description: Long years of stability come to an end when Shiny Mega Gardevoir-EX lays siege to the mighty Gear Palace with a host of greedy forces. The Mythical Steam Pokémon Volcanion must wield the dual powers of fire and water to stop them! As the battle rages, Xerneas BREAK and Yveltal BREAK face off in the Pokémon TCG: XY—Steam Siege expansion!

308861955.name: XY—Steam Siege Evolution Pack
308861955.description: A 23-card XY—Steam Siege Evolution pack, including 1 of 4 unique foil promo cards.

GearsofFireBundle.name: Gears of Fire
GearsofFireBundle.description: Spin up a great engine of battle with the Mythical Pokémon Volcanion! Combine the steely determination of Klinklang with the leaping speed of Monferno, and seize the power of steam. All aboard the victory train!

GearsofFirePCD.name: Gears of Fire
GearsofFirePCD.description: Spin up a great engine of battle with the Mythical Pokémon Volcanion! Combine the steely determination of Klinklang with the leaping speed of Monferno, and seize the power of steam. All aboard the victory train!

MagearnaFallTin2016.name: Heart's Shield
MagearnaFallTin2016.description: While protecting your team with the mystic power of Magearna-EX, you can use this deck's Metal and Shield Energy to power up Mawile and Cobalion. Sharpen the edge of your attack with the Heart's Shield deck!

PikachuFallTin2016.name: Thunder's Crash
PikachuFallTin2016.description: Spin up that powerful little dynamo, Pikachu-EX, and switch on full power! The Thunder's Crash deck uses Magnezone and Pikachu-EX to create a massive charge—and big damage. Add Clemont and Misty's Determination to keep rolling strong!

RingofLightningBundle.name: Ring of Lightning
RingofLightningBundle.description: Bring forth lightning and psychic shocks with the Mythical Pokémon Hoopa! Galvantula's electric webs and the surging power of Ampharos keep the current flowing and give your opponent quite a shock. Call down the thunder!

RingofLightningPCD.name: Ring of Lightning
RingofLightningPCD.description: Bring forth lightning and psychic shocks with the Mythical Pokémon Hoopa! Galvantula's electric webs and the surging power of Ampharos keep the current flowing and give your opponent quite a shock. Call down the thunder!

VolcanionFallTin2016.name: Mountain's Fury
VolcanionFallTin2016.description: Follow a fiery path with Volcanion-EX! Trainer cards help keep your hand fueled up, while Blaziken's Spreading Flames attack stokes those fires and keeps the streak going, so you can burn twice as hot with the Mountain's Fury deck!
